Package: aiddataviz
Title: Data Visualization Themes and Tools for AidData
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Teal", "Emery", , "lte@tealinsights.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools, themes, and color palettes for creating consistent, accessible, and on-brand data visualizations using 'ggplot2'. Built for AidData at the College of William & Mary, this package implements the official William & Mary brand guidelines while adhering to data visualization best practices. Features include custom ggplot2 themes, color palettes optimized for accessibility, and functions for creating publication-ready visualizations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
